            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="video" MadCap:conditions="General.Server-Only">
            <p class="buttonT32-play"><a href="https://youtu.be/_DO8AaXjRUo" data-lity="true" class="buttonT32-play-link">WATCH&#160;THE&#160;VIDEO (Templates and Styles)</a>
